<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498076.jpg" alt="Entrepreneurs gather at Indaba in Cape Town" width="300" height="400" rel="">click to enlargeThe event takes on the format of a full-day conference with plenary sessions and networking breaks throughout the day. More than eight entrepreneurial experts and talented business minds will share their stories, growth strategies, tips, tools and ideas for personal and business growth. The agenda include topics such as goal setting, product idea evaluation, market needs, growth strategies, branding and marketing, finding more customers, sales and much more. Although the event and agenda is designed for owners of established smme’s and entrepreneurs, start-ups and owners of larger businesses are welcome and will also benefit. Delegates will expand their knowledge base through keynotes from speakers like Preetesh Sewraj (Product of the Year SA), Dr. Madelaine Gomes (Executive Business and Mindset Coach), Steve Reid (Centre for Entrepreneurship Director at False Bay College), Shukri Toefy (entrepreneurship expert with the Entrepreneurship Centre at Saïd Business School, University of Oxford), Axel Rittershaus (International Executive Coach) and many other subject experts. Attending the event is a great way to keep up with the latest trends, learn new skills, get new ideas for growing your business, discover new strategies and meet fellow business owners. The Wholesale and Retail SETA (W&RSETA) will participate in the Entrepreneurs Indaba to promote and encourage small businesses to participate in the skills development process. They will further use the opportunity to educate small businesses of the W&RSETA and the opportunities available through its skills development programmes.<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498079.jpg" alt="Barrie Swart" width="148" height="223">Barrie Swart<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498080.jpg" alt="Axel Rittershaus" width="222" height="223">Axel Rittershaus<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498081.jpg" alt="Steve Reid" width="314" height="223">Steve Reid<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498082.jpg" alt="Shukri Toefy" width="218" height="223">Shukri Toefy<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498083.jpg" alt="Dr Madelaine Gomes" width="210" height="211">Dr Madelaine Gomes<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498084.jpg" alt="Preetesh Sewraj" width="294" height="211">Preetesh Sewraj<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498085.jpg" alt="Lauren Kinghorn" width="189" height="211">Lauren Kinghorn<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498086.jpg" alt="Heather Cresswell" width="206" height="211">Heather CresswellThe event takes place at the Garden Court Nelson Mandela Blvd Hotel in Woodstock, Cape Town. The event also offers marketing opportunities for suppliers.Tickets are available online at www.entrepreneursindaba.co.za or by calling the organiser, CADEK Media, on 021 854 4700.